branchCategory.name: 10/11/21/22-CU
branchCategory.description: <P>The series CU free mount, clean room cylinder saves space and allows direct and precise mounting. It is available in 6mm to 25mm bore sizes with stroke lengths up to 50mm. The CU series is a single rod, single acting cylinder with rubber bumpers as standard, and is auto switch capable.</P>
